{
  "stem": "6130.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think we still had a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we went into a ambulatory, which was really stupid, because sick people were always shot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we didn't-- there was-- there were beds there-- cots.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And my sister and I-- my sister lied on there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And Yutka, my niece, and I went under the sheet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But we were so thin that it didn't show that we were under the sheet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because that woman who liked me so much, you know, who I was her maid, came hollering.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Magda, Magda, [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where are you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Magda?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Magda-- screaming.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't say a word.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She could see my sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she asked, where are they?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You'll never see them again if you don't tell me, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was touching with her feet, our feet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] She didn't see me under the sheet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Can you believe how thin I was?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So she left, and the Germans left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there we were, about nine of us-- us three, and there were six others who escape.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So now, everything is absolutely quiet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Of course, we stayed there like statues.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We don't dare to move, because you never knew who would show up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I think the next day, we started to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we started to walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We didn't know where are we going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had absolutely no way of-- no way of knowing where we were or where are we going.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And on the way, we met a German soldier with a gun.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he asked us, who-- who you are?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "What are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we said, we got lost.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He could have shot us, but he left.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
